  (1) You are not an Enterprise (as defined in Section 2).
  (2) You do not operate a Competing SaaS / Hosted Service (as defined in Section 2).

B. Contributor Commercial Waiver
In appreciation of community support, any verified Contributor is granted a perpetual, 
